channel.title: CVE Feed for Dell EMC -- Dell EMC IsilonSD Management Server
channel.description: The latest CVEs for Dell EMC -- Dell EMC IsilonSD Management Server

item.title: CVE-2019-3709|2024-08-04T19:19:17.423Z -- dell%20emc -- dell%20emc%20isilonsd%20management%20server
item.description: IsilonSD Management Server 1.1.0 contains a cross-site scripting vulnerability while registering vCenter servers. A remote attacker can trick an admin user to potentially exploit this vulnerability to execute malicious HTML or JavaScript code in the context of the admin user.

item.title: CVE-2019-3708|2024-08-04T19:19:17.689Z -- dell%20emc -- dell%20emc%20isilonsd%20management%20server
item.description: IsilonSD Management Server 1.1.0 contains a cross-site scripting vulnerability while uploading an OVA file. A remote attacker can trick an admin user to potentially exploit this vulnerability to execute malicious HTML or JavaScript code in the context of the admin user.
